comments: Adams (OKC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Harden (HOU) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
RAR shows Tucker (HOU) grabs Grant's (OKC) arm during the rebound and affects his ability to get to the ball.
LAR shows Gordon (HOU) makes marginal contact with George (OKC) at the end of his drive.
LLB shows Westbrook (OKC) initiates some contact with Tucker (HOU) at the end of his drive but goes to and not through him.
Paul (HOU) makes marginal contact with Schroder (OKC) on the perimeter.
Harden (HOU) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Schroder (OKC).
Harden (HOU) holds Schroder (OKC) after the initial contact on the screen and affects his ability to separate and defend the play.
Paul (HOU) initiates some contact with Ferguson (OKC) on the perimeter but does not dislodge him.
Harden (HOU) is firming up in legal position during the pick  with Ferguson (OKC).
Ferguson (OKC) briefly places his arm around Harden (HOU) on the perimeter but does not affect his FOM.
Ferguson (OKC) makes contact to the arm of Harden (HOU) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
George (OKC) delivers marginal contact while setting the pick on Gordon (HOU).
Adams (OKC) and Capela (HOU) engage and disengage off-ball during the pass in the lane.
Adams (OKC) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Tucker (HOU).
Tucker (HOU) engages with Westbrook (OKC) following the pick but does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Harden (HOU) is firming up in legal position during the pick with Schroder (OKC).
Schroder (OKC) briefly slides his arm around Harden (HOU) as they disengage from the pick.
Paul (HOU) gathers the ball and takes two legal steps.
Tucker (HOU) extends his arm and makes contact to Westbrook's (OKC) thigh during his upward shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Paul (HOU) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
George (OKC) makes contact to the body of Harden (HOU) on the drive that affects his SQBR.
RAR shows Tucker (HOU) maintains legal position as George (OKC) loses his balance while attempting to retrieve the inbound pass.
Adams (OKC) is firming up in legal position during the screen with Gordon (HOU).
Westbrook (OKC) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Gordon (HOU) makes marginal contact with Westbrook (OKC) but does not affect his ability to pass.
Tucker (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by George (OKC).
Harden (HOU) extends his arm into George (OKC) and affects his ability to defend during the inbound pass.
Tucker (HOU) slightly extends his arm into Grant (OKC) during the screen but the contact is marginal.
George (OKC) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Harden (HOU).
